        h4
            strong Students with Disabilities
        p Johns Hopkins University is committed to providing reasonable and appropriate accommodations to students with disabilities. Students with documented disabilities should contact the coordinator listed on the #[a(href="https://advanced.jhu.edu/current-students/current-students-resources/disability-accommodations/") the Disability Accommodations] page. Further information and a link to the Student Request for Accommodation form can also be found on #[a(href="https://advanced.jhu.edu/current-students/current-students-resources/disability-accommodations/") the Disability Accommodations] page.
