        p To better support all students, the Johns Hopkins University non-academic #[a(href="https://studentaffairs.jhu.edu/policies/student-code/") Student Conduct Code] has been integrated and updated to include all divisions of the University. In addition, it is important to note that all AAP students are still accountable for the #[a(href="https://advanced.jhu.edu/current-students/policies/code-of-conduct/") Code of Conduct for Advanced Academic Programs].

